{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"411 Length Required","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/411","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">HyperText Transfer Protocol (HTTP) 411 Length Required 클라이언트 오류 응답 코드는 서버가 정의된 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Length\"><code>Content-Length</code></a> 헤더 없이 요청을 수락하지 않음을 나타낸다.</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>참고: 사양별로 청크 시리즈로 데이터를 전송할 때 <code>Content-Length</code> 헤더가 생략되며, 각 청크의 시작 부분에서 현재 청크의 길이를 16진수 형식으로 추가해야 한다. 자세한 내용은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Transfer-Encoding\"><code>Transfer-Encoding</code></a>을(를) 참조하십시오.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"상태","title":"상태","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">411 Length Required</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"정의","title":"정의","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Title</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7231#section-6.5.10\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 7231, section 6.5.10: 411 Length Required</a></td>\n   <td>Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP/1.1): Semantics and Content</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"참고","title":"참고","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Length\"><code>Content-Length</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Transfer-Encoding\"><code>Transfer-Encoding</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"상태","id":"상태"},{"text":"정의","id":"정의"},{"text":"참고","id":"참고"}],"summary":"","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"411 Length Required","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"411 Length Required","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"ti